<section class="border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent-600">
          How we work
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">
          A focused team, at the size you need.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          Datagrove engages as a subcontractor to firms running larger programmes,
          and as a direct delivery team for companies that want one technical
          partner. The work is hands-on, the team stays small, and the people
          delivering are the people you talked to.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <figure>
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=85"
            alt="A laptop showing analytics dashboards next to a notebook on a desk."
            width="1600"
            height="1067"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="aspect-[3/2] w-full rounded-2xl object-cover ring-1 ring-slate-200 shadow-sm"
          />
          <figcaption class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-400">
            Photo by Carlos Muza on Unsplash.
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
